# Policy: PRIVATE repo. Track the evidence + the LLM-written summary docs.
# Keep local-only: the .env secret, oversized media, generated/derived artifacts,
# and the folders involving claimed minors.

# --- Secret ---
.env

# --- Oversized evidence ---
# Files >100MB exceed GitHub's hard per-file limit. They are bundled into
# oversized_evidence.zip (kept local) by _bundle.py. The zip itself is too big to push.
oversized_evidence.zip

# --- Scratch scripts, extracted-archive mirror, generated indexes ---
# Everything underscore-prefixed at the repo root is local tooling/output:
#   _scan*.py, _apply_renames.py, _update_refs.py, _bundle.py (scratch scripts)
#   _unpacked/ (extraction of the archive zips - duplicates source, regenerable)
#   _fileindex.txt, _transcribe_work/ (generated)
/_*

# --- Derived / regenerable artifacts ---
# Whisper transcripts and OCR dumps are machine-generated from the source media
# (via transcribe.py / make_transcripts.py). Kept local to avoid re-coupling the
# repo to a fragile path-encoded reference graph.
/transcripts/
/ocr_dump_original.txt
/ocr_dump_unpacked.txt
/TRANSCRIPTS.md

# --- Sensitive: claimed minors stay local, never committed ---
/Pedo claims involving supposed 16yo/
/Myzzl claims to be 18 and age baiting adults and cuddling a 15yo and 20yo. claims to be 14 after confrontation. 20yo makes sexual comments to 15yo/
